race.comment: OLIVER GRANDE (1) collided in the run and missed the frame when fourth (30.13) at this track over 509m in a OPEN. Should be in this for a long way. HE'S SUITED (7) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 29.80 beating Durango Monelli. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. One of the prime contenders. FLASH CODE (8) was narrowly beaten when placing two back but missed the frame latest finishing sixth (30.60) in a Grade 5/6 at this track. Expected to do much better this time. NEW HOPE (3) placed last time and is worth some thought.
